OL,5, The Blue singer Lee Ryan has been      
OL,6, convicted of the racially aggravated   
OL,7, assault of a flight cabin crew member. 
OL,9,FRyan, 39, had drunk a bottle of port in
OL,10,Fthe airport lounge before boarding a   
OL,11,FBritish Airways flight from Glasgow to 
OL,12,FLondon City Airport on 31 July, Ealing 
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court heard.              
OL,15,FOne flight crew member said the pop    
OL,16,Fstar had told her he wanted an upgrade 
OL,17,Fand asked her if she knew who he was.  
OL,19,FRyan, who denied all charges, said his 
OL,20,Fbehaviour had been "playful".          
